SUMMARY:Interchange Message: WHITECHAPEL STATION: Monday 26 May until 
 Sunday 8 June\, no direct lift service between the ticket hall and Lower 
 Concourse. Alternative lifts for step-free access between the ticket 
 hall\, Lower Concourse\, Elizabeth line and Windrush line will be 
 available to complete your journey.
END:VEVENT
